@node "Technical Information" "Technical Information"

 Technical Information
 =====================

   DiskFull supports at least 2500 files per files-list.
 If you have to operate longer than this value consider to use the
 MOVE option (see @{"Options" link "Options" 0}) then make a new files-list
 for all remaining files (the MOVE option delete original files
 after the copy to disk!).



 See @{"Registration" link "Registration" 0} for more info


@endnode

